Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 11/07/2025

At Story World, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our Facebook app.

Information We Collect
We may collect the following information:

Your public Facebook profile (name, profile picture, etc.)

Your Facebook user ID

Any permissions you grant (e.g., email address)

We do not collect sensitive personal data or share your data with third parties.

How We Use Your Information
We use the information to:

Personalize your app experience

Improve our content and features

Communicate with you if necessary

We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data.

Data Storage and Security
All data is stored securely, and we take all reasonable steps to protect it from unauthorized access or disclosure.

Third-Party Services
We do not integrate with third-party services that collect personal information beyond what Facebook provides through permissions.
